> I&#x27;m pretty sure those and a bunch more are taunts for yordles in general, not Teemo specifically, since he says things like:
> 
>  &quot;Just &#x27;cause we was kin don&#x27;t mean I ain&#x27;t feeding you to Skaarl!&quot;
>  &quot;Hey cous&#x27;, glad you came to visit!&quot;
>  &quot;A relative&#x27;s just another unwanted guest.&quot;
>  &quot;Afraid I had to cut your visit short.&quot;
>  &quot;You ain&#x27;t cute now!&quot;
>  &quot;Aw, you are so cute... &#x27;fore I ripped your fuzzy head off!&quot;
>  &quot;I could feel bad about killing you, or we could stomp on your corpse!&quot;
>  &quot;You was cute - lousy, but cute.&quot;
> 
> All of this comes after taunts for Talon, so it could be Teemo, or yordles in general. I&#x27;m inclined to say it&#x27;s for yordles in general.

I'll bet the "Cut your visit short" line is specifically aimed at Veigar.
